  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/729990/extras/9afb2a73483b1e4ee38df7d723db293a.webp?t=1510934386\" width=246 height=37 /></span><br>Hexopods is the frenetic twin-stick shooter for hardcore players! Try to beat your friends or an AI in this multiplayer bullet hell! Adapt your experience as you please with its modular game modes for infinite replayability!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/729990/extras/f3ff67c3b4cfd8334484941905d5f264.webp?t=1510934386\" width=207 height=37 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 4 different ships with unique playstyles<br></li><li> Fast and intense fights!<br></li><li> 4 different adaptable maps<br></li><li> Hard to play, Impossible to master<br></li><li> No random, only skill to win!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/729990/extras/085381745b484cdea3da4e050219c52c.webp?t=1510934386\" width=434 height=37 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Multiple lives for each player<br></li><li> A timeout with a shrinking arena!<br></li><li> Power-ups on the map<br></li><li> A moving \"king of the hill\" with customizable reward<br></li><li> An hexagonal shield rotating around your ship!</li></ul>And many more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/729990/extras/036b44639ee798d06f582e4320bd376c.avif?t=1510934386\" width=616 height=353 /></span>",
